and they have their own set of volume,
mutes, solos, panning,

00:11:26.820 --> 00:11:32.580
and DSP inserts for complete and total
integration into the production process.

00:11:32.740 --> 00:11:33.540
So that's fantastic.

00:11:33.640 --> 00:11:36.640
And of course,
everything on the integrated

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:38.640
mixing console is fully,
fully automated.

