people like yourselves to create

00:13:10.920 --> 00:13:16.640
amazing and innovative plug-ins that
can immediately be integrated right

00:13:16.640 --> 00:13:22.390
alongside Logic's own plug-ins for even
more of a wide variety of sounds and DSP.

00:13:24.620 --> 00:13:29.360
So basically Logic Pro 6 is probably
one of the most flexible music

